  <brief_title>Evaluation of HIV-1, HCV and HBV Blood Screening Tests With Human Blood Donor Specimens</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of a TMA Assay for the Screening of HIV-1 RNA, HCV RNA and HBV DNA in Human Blood Donor Plasma Specimens</official_title>
  <sponsors>
