  <source>Novartis</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to validate the performance characteristics of an assay that
      tests for HIV-1, HCV and HBV on an automated blood bank instrument for registration
      submission.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
